Snowreap 17, 12 Portal Year<br />
<br />
<b>Verdantine 19, 13 Portal Year</b><br />
Blimy has it been a year already?  How did the time go so fast?  I stopped fer a drink one night and a year later I find meself at the same bar in Glenden Wood.
